summary: In his last v live Tae was talking how glad he is dat the company finally has given them more time to rest aka he is deffinetly...
question: In his last v live Tae was talking how glad he is dat the company finally has given them more time to rest aka he is deffinetly vocal about not liking the fact that they legit have no free time for themselves for there hobbys . diva is a harsh word i think he meant a really vocal person couse the virgos gang are hard workers ,the libra will just want balace but the capricorn will def complane couse they have so much hidden in them  idk just my thoughts
answer:
It really seems like the company gives them more time to rest and enjoy the cities they stay in too. Like this time in America. It seemed like they all got to go around and explore. Also Hoseok said in his Vlive that he’s doing really well and also sleeping a lot. It wasn’t always like that.

I think they might have made some demands to BigHit, when they renewed their contract last year. They also talked about disbanding, and maybe it was because they felt like they were about to be worned out.. I think it’s really good that Taehyung and the others express their feelings on what they aren’t happy with..

summary: Tae is under so much pressure i HATE the fans that tell him he shoud cut his care and not grow beard couse they dont find it...
question: Tae is under so much pressure i HATE the fans that tell him he shoud cut his care and not grow beard couse they dont find it attractive , or getting angry at the thought that he might smoke all tho it was a pastel pencil holder like all the bitches need to stop attaking him! his is a cap ,korean its so difficult for him to actioly do what he wants couse people will jump on him and say you are disrespecting the fans ,like bitch what?anyway i am getting aangry sorry <3 i just want them free
answer:
I think the guys focus way too much on what their fans think of their appearance. I’ve heard them several times say that they like their natural hair the best, but if the fans wants to see crazy colors they will dye it.

Like it’s their face and body and they should choose for themselves, rather than for other people. If Tae wants to grow out his hair or beard then let him.

The whole smoking thing was too much lmao. Smoking is an awful addiction. I’m a smoker myself and I wish that I never started, because it’s so hard to quit. But Taehyung is a grown up and he can do what he wants.

Many Army’s really feel like they own the guys, and it’s healthy for anyone that they feel that way!
